OL,6, millions of people are coping with the 
OL,7, uncertainty of whether their benefits  
OL,8, will rise with inflation.              
OL,10,FIn Sunderland, where one in 13 of the  
OL,11,Fworking-age population claims          
OL,12,Fout-of-work benefits, Nicky and Alison 
OL,13,Fare struggling to survive.             
OL,15,F"I'm freezing right now, I'm shivering 
OL,16,Fwhile I'm on dialysis, but I won't put 
OL,17,Fthe heating on because it's too        
OL,18,Fexpensive," says Nicky Telford.        
